title: The unexpected Tudors
itunes:title: The unexpected Tudors
itunes:subtitle: Sam Willis and James Daybell take a sideways look at the Tudors era, exploring everything from gloves to priest holes. Historyextra.com/podcast
description:
Historians Sam Willis and James Daybell, creators of the Histories of the Unexpected books and podcast, take a sideways look at the Tudors era, exploring everything from gloves to priest holes. Historyextra.com/podcast
